{"tid":25601,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"係間精神病復康者社企做過一年，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-06T08:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:59:28.000Z","uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6be33627aa00d31d4f66223e947d2c7a872ae1","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"會自爆同影響到公司/同事唔答<br />\n點解會做：入職前幾年長期失眠訓唔好就去睇精神科醫生，之後醫生話有份工既話可能會訓得好D，咁就比個醫生同社工一腳踢左入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e720c8506ab989e19aa374a7f181064e9d15d480","tid":25601,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c51162eba8df0f1d8fc04795aca232d01c62474","tid":25601,"uid":55695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"點解會訓得好D"},{"pid":"daa0862b5d0addf364bed13980336353f90957c7","tid":25601,"uid":57665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"NLPRA?"},{"pid":"af811d20352380b4f09b01fe73412e5cde365765","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會訓得好D</blockquote><br />\n個陣岩岩讀完書做緊廢青，醫生話可能生活習慣日夜癲倒搞到訓得差，有份正常工會好D<br />\n（個陣廢青已經被分類做精神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但係我返個份工仲日夜癲倒過廢青囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efa1fdef1d39ec98f3f02cdfc4109cf6350d635","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>NLPRA?</blockquote><br />\n呢個會係幫精神病人搵工，應該唔少社企做緊既人都係佢轉介<br />\n利伸，唔係呢個會，但同事同呢個會有關"},{"pid":"fb81e4c7cd9c856024a95562614cf33ad515c24f","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請不請人</blockquote><br />\n公司好多種類既工，唔知邊樣岩你，但係社工轉介會快d，但人工真係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780531b45a8db811ae6cad1330723efea864852f","tid":25601,"uid":18761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"啲痴線撚有無暴力傾向"},{"pid":"14ad9ee9d9a8024118b0df3975466703b1d0e2f3","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲痴線撚有無暴力傾向</blockquote><br />\n有食藥之下好多同事都同正常人無分別，同埋間公司都會睇你覺得用唔用得著<br />\n但係有時有d同事心情差或者無食藥會dum野或者做sales個d罵下客咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上都好和平<br />\n要搞到上新聞既就一定無<br />\n反而你驚下平時你身邊d人可能仲有嚴重既精神病"},{"pid":"144f96620323edde1ab632d76d1d35147659a7dc","tid":25601,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:27:10.000Z","msg":"新生會？"},{"pid":"ee7ed6dcf5c323b4420f402b201c2d6891b15a19","tid":25601,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6be33627aa00d31d4f66223e947d2c7a872ae1","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"會自爆同影響到公司/同事唔答<br />\n點解會做：入職前幾年長期失眠訓唔好就去睇精神科醫生，之後醫生話有份工既話可能會訓得好D，咁就比個醫生同社工一腳踢左入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"TG傾傾？<br />\n有野想穩你幫手"},{"pid":"3eb603e0f70c26ad64df3ef9c1d5ba696c1059ca","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee7ed6dcf5c323b4420f402b201c2d6891b15a19","tid":25601,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6be33627aa00d31d4f66223e947d2c7a872ae1","tid":25601,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"會自爆同影響到公司/同事唔答<br />\n點解會做：入職前幾年長期失眠訓唔好就去睇精神科醫生，之後醫生話有份工既話可能會訓得好D，咁就比個醫生同社工一腳踢左入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 